<span id="freeTextContainer12623936296668179978">Oh my god. I started this at my sister&apos;s house one night, then had to finish the pointless &quot;Stolen Boy&quot;, so I just got back to it yesterday. I could not put the thing down. Each of the four sections was so intense and exciting and terrifying. And FINALLY: an author who messes with form in a minimalist way that has real purpose and expression. Take that, Dave Eggers! Take that, Jonathan Safron Foer or whoever! This book broke my heart every page. It deserves every award it has won and then some. </span>
